text:
Y’all this isn’t on topic but you see how when K-pop idols aren’t around most of us fantasize about ships and stuff but when the idols are watching no one dares name a ship. For example. Every time hyunjin is seen with felix it’s “oh hyunlix are so cute!❤” or “I hope they become a couple omg!❤”  ships aren’t ok. You can’t be shipping JenLisa just because they are best friends? Imagine you were an idol. And you were being shipped with your least favorite member or like your closest member as a friend? What would you think about it? Please spread the word. Stop shipping idols and invading their privacy. Don’t act like you didn’t see soyeon get uncomfortable when she saw a fan making them all kiss as cartoon characters. Idols should be protected. Not be shipped and spread rumors about. I get their close but it doesn’t give you the right to ship them..if your also not okay with this spread the hashtag #STOPSHIPINGIDOLS because if you do ship idols your a saesaeng whether you like it or not. Thanks for reading,spread the word/JJAM(pun intended),free Palestine and thank you very much!❤
